<!-- ASCII NOTE -------------------- -->
<p class="asciinote">
<pre> </pre> <!--...for vertical space on a tty print...-->
Note: If you are reading the text (ASCII) version of this page
(doc/README-GemplusApduio.txt), be informed that there is an
