<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0"><tr><td>

   <h3 class="index">Features</h3>

</td></tr><tr><td>
<img src="../../../images/ArtFolderFull.gif" alt="Features">
</td></tr></table>
<!-- ------------------------------- -->

<p>
The Gemplus Apduio CardTerminal is an implementation
of an OCF CardTerminal to access the Java Card 2.1.2 Simulator
distributed by Sun Microsystems in its
<a href="http://java.sun.com/products/javacard/dev_kit.html">
Java Card 2.1.2 Development Kit</a> 

